snippet.title: Rise Of Humanity - Gameplay Long Feb 2020
snippet.description:
Early access coming in 2021

In Rise of Humanity players will gather, upgrade and combine cards, recruit new heroes as others meet their unfortunate demise and discover new strategies by completing missions in an attempt to stop the remnant of project hivemind.


Join our discord! https://discord.gg/riseofhumanity
Follow us on Twitter! https://twitter.com/riseofhumangame
Like us on Facebook! https://www.facebook.com/RiseOfHumanityGame
Join us on Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/riseofhumanity/


Check our website!  http://riseofhumanitygame.com/


A game by Cybernetic Walrus! http://www.cyberneticwalrus.com
